{"type":"message","id":"95471b81","parentId":"0bf7bdac","timestamp":"2026-02-15T11:43:28.453Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Deleting the Method**\n\nI've decided to remove the `get_wax_price` method from the `MockRedis` class. The rationale is to simplify the mock and reduce its dependencies, focusing it on core Redis functionality. The removal will streamline testing and reduce potential for unexpected behavior within the mock object.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"edit_1771155808446_454","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"    async def get_sales_history(self, title: str) -> List[float]:\n        base_price = random.uniform(5.0, 50.0)\n        return [base_price * (1 + random.uniform(-0.1, 0.1)) for _ in range(20)]\n\nclass HybridEngine:","oldText":"    async def get_sales_history(self, title: str) -> List[float]:\n        base_price = random.uniform(5.0, 50.0)\n        return [base_price * (1 + random.uniform(-0.1, 0.1)) for _ in range(20)]\n\n    async def get_wax_price(self, title: str) -> Decimal:\n        if random.random() > 0.8:\n            return Decimal(str(random.uniform(10.0, 100.0)))\n        return Decimal(\"0\")\n\nclass HybridEngine:","file_path":"DMarket-Telegram-Bot-main/src/core/engine.py"},"thoughtSignature":"CikBjz1rX0cRn7ZFe+wj1ICKm2dO2+TSJToXRgF1GO2xMEwnMeS6cpoCLgpDAY89a1/yjv2rwwVVr8lWG0Awv++bxd28o/8eXoOBqHai43xrsxhNd5w9TwinY8E3UiyWE3xgt2UX1dmDYWYmh0LYwQ=="}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":28827,"output":257,"cacheRead":25643,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29084,"cost":{"input":0.057654,"output":0.003084,"cacheRead":0.0051286000000000005,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0658666}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771155803477}}
