{"type":"message","id":"f752aeb5","parentId":"3d5b694b","timestamp":"2026-02-15T11:45:10.244Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering Refactor**\n\nI'm currently focused on the `UnifiedStrategyManager` within the `dmarket/unified_strategy_system.py` file. The goal is to refactor it. I am evaluating the current structure to identify areas that would benefit from simplification and improved efficiency.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"edit_1771155910238_469","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"\nclass UnifiedStrategyManager:\n    \"\"\"Менеджер для управления всеми стратегиями.\"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(\n        self,\n        dmarket_api: \"DMarketAPI\",\n    ) -> None:\n        \"\"\"Инициализация менеджера.\n\n        Args:\n            dmarket_api: DMarket API клиент\n        \"\"\"\n        self.dmarket_api = dmarket_api\n\n        # Инициализируем все стратегии\n        self._strategies: dict[StrategyType, IFindingStrategy] = {}\n        self._init_strategies()\n\n        logger.info(\n            \"unified_strategy_manager_initialized\",\n            strategies_count=len(self._strategies),\n        )\n\n    def _init_strategies(self) -> None:\n        \"\"\"Инициализировать все доступные стратегии.\"\"\"\n        # Float Value Arbitrage\n        self._strategies[StrategyType.FLOAT_VALUE_ARBITRAGE] = FloatValueArbitrageStrategy(\n            dmarket_api=self.dmarket_api\n        )\n","oldText":"\nclass UnifiedStrategyManager:\n    \"\"\"Менеджер для управления всеми стратегиями.\"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(\n        self,\n        dmarket_api: \"DMarketAPI\",\n        waxpeer_api: \"WaxpeerAPI | None\" = None,\n    ) -> None:\n        \"\"\"Инициализация менеджера.\n\n        Args:\n            dmarket_api: DMarket API клиент\n            waxpeer_api: Waxpeer API клиент (опционально)\n        \"\"\"\n        self.dmarket_api = dmarket_api\n        self.waxpeer_api = waxpeer_api\n\n        # Инициализируем все стратегии\n        self._strategies: dict[StrategyType, IFindingStrategy] = {}\n        self._init_strategies()\n\n        logger.info(\n            \"unified_strategy_manager_initialized\",\n            strategies_count=len(self._strategies),\n        )\n\n    def _init_strategies(self) -> None:\n        \"\"\"Инициализировать все доступные стратегии.\"\"\"\n        # Cross-platform (DMarket → Waxpeer)\n        self._strategies[StrategyType.CROSS_PLATFORM_ARBITRAGE] = CrossPlatformArbitrageStrategy(\n            dmarket_api=self.dmarket_api,\n            waxpeer_api=self.waxpeer_api,\n        )\n\n        # Float Value Arbitrage\n        self._strategies[StrategyType.FLOAT_VALUE_ARBITRAGE] = FloatValueArbitrageStrategy(\n            dmarket_api=self.dmarket_api\n        )\n","file_path":"DMarket-Telegram-Bot-main/src/dmarket/unified_strategy_system.py"},"thoughtSignature":"CikBjz1rXx/1S55NpgDySSGTp/tsiZs5LGXm5X2dLP7RH8a7eJw/EF0OMwpZAY89a19lL1CEmtKMggc1gJf1BiETxImKqiGzlG6kC1ayXbRokzjBEHW8hoDCnxc4LuhqTg5+as8uRx3iZmsBM0plzywN5Q5vfgzYRScFlSnQeYufatjwH/0KSQGPPWtfrc+Iyaa0o21I0Aom4VcZB02Izs3fjXanCCDp9ahYIazEowgnHBpT2qiK4mBpJMfTWRYRshSvgp0sj724zNFNSwlnF6k="}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":61252,"output":635,"cacheRead":56908,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61887,"cost":{"input":0.12250399999999999,"output":0.00762,"cacheRead":0.0113816,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.14150559999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771155902069}}
