{"type":"message","id":"5ec78299","parentId":"6d1d3ffc","timestamp":"2026-02-15T11:45:58.991Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Deleting Configuration Updates**\n\nI've just removed the call to `_update_waxpeer_from_env` within the `config.py` file. This should streamline the configuration process. My next step will be to test the impact of this change on the bot's functionality.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"edit_1771155958979_477","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"    def _update_from_env(self) -> None:\n        \"\"\"Update configuration from environment variables.\"\"\"\n        # Update each config section using helper methods (Phase 2 refactoring)\n        self._update_bot_from_env()\n        self._update_dmarket_from_env()\n        self._update_trading_from_env()\n\n        # Environment","file_path":"DMarket-Telegram-Bot-main/src/utils/config.py","oldText":"    def _update_from_env(self) -> None:\n        \"\"\"Update configuration from environment variables.\"\"\"\n        # Update each config section using helper methods (Phase 2 refactoring)\n        self._update_bot_from_env()\n        self._update_dmarket_from_env()\n        self._update_trading_from_env()\n        self._update_waxpeer_from_env()\n\n        # Environment"},"thoughtSignature":"CikBjz1rX6XviuoZ8itvRzOMkWpJtmAF9dLEL1rbdiLF4qNjQaxuZxWa/gpKAY89a1/HcCht26fS/CzVUMvHztCu2vdpYK32c9PLqb/ZWVAo3U1hKSZXTt6VKTwPkNzjZQXQmMCm2/s58s45ZzpJVVtEs/mavC8KTwGPPWtfLkzOtcVuzKe6MknFK4mzRi74NlzopkBE2inl5H/IPXduGLGXMmiXhXe3MkBefg2/UcPFMkGfzVl1H6xlajlpKRARKZ8LvzlWnAc="}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":74023,"output":236,"cacheRead":70036,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74259,"cost":{"input":0.14804599999999998,"output":0.002832,"cacheRead":0.014007200000000001,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.16488519999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771155953785}}
