{"type":"message","id":"7760e854","parentId":"0438c5b3","timestamp":"2026-02-15T11:50:23.106Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering Class Initialization Changes**\n\nI'm currently working on refactoring the `__init__` method. The goal is to eliminate the `waxpeer_api` dependency, streamlining the setup process. This should simplify instantiation and potentially improve the overall modularity of the class. The focus is to make the class initialization cleaner and more adaptable.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"edit_1771156223095_515","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"    def __init__(\n        self,\n        dmarket_api: DMarketAPI,\n        steam_api: SteamAPI | None = None,\n        min_profit_percent: Decimal = MIN_PROFIT_PERCENT,\n        min_liquidity_score: int = MIN_LIQUIDITY_SCORE,\n        enable_dmarket_arbitrage: bool = True,\n        enable_cross_platform: bool = True,\n    ):\n        \"\"\"Initialize integrated arbitrage scanner.\n\n        Args:\n            dmarket_api: DMarket API client\n            steam_api: Steam API client (optional)\n            min_profit_percent: Minimum profit percentage to consider\n            min_liquidity_score: Minimum liquidity score (1-3)\n            enable_dmarket_arbitrage: Enable DMarket-only arbitrage\n            enable_cross_platform: Enable cross-platform arbitrage\n        \"\"\"\n        self.dmarket = dmarket_api\n        self.steam = steam_api\n        self.min_profit_percent = min_profit_percent\n        self.min_liquidity_score = min_liquidity_score\n        self.enable_dmarket_arbitrage = enable_dmarket_arbitrage\n        self.enable_cross_platform = enable_cross_platform\n\n        # Storage for discovered opportunities and listing targets\n        self.opportunities: list[ArbitrageOpportunity] = []\n        self.dmarket_only_opportunities: list[dict[str, Any]] = []  # DMarket-only arbitrage\n        self.listing_targets: dict[str, Any] = {}  # asset_id -> target","file_path":"DMarket-Telegram-Bot-main/src/dmarket/integrated_arbitrage_scanner.py","oldText":"    def __init__(\n        self,\n        dmarket_api: DMarketAPI,\n        waxpeer_api: WaxpeerAPI,\n        steam_api: SteamAPI | None = None,\n        min_profit_percent: Decimal = MIN_PROFIT_PERCENT,\n        min_liquidity_score: int = MIN_LIQUIDITY_SCORE,\n        enable_dmarket_arbitrage: bool = True,\n        enable_cross_platform: bool = True,\n    ):\n        \"\"\"Initialize integrated arbitrage scanner.\n\n        Args:\n            dmarket_api: DMarket API client\n            waxpeer_api: Waxpeer API client\n            steam_api: Steam API client (optional)\n            min_profit_percent: Minimum profit percentage to consider\n            min_liquidity_score: Minimum liquidity score (1-3)\n            enable_dmarket_arbitrage: Enable DMarket-only arbitrage\n            enable_cross_platform: Enable cross-platform arbitrage\n        \"\"\"\n        self.dmarket = dmarket_api\n        self.waxpeer = waxpeer_api\n        self.steam = steam_api\n        self.min_profit_percent = min_profit_percent\n        self.min_liquidity_score = min_liquidity_score\n        self.enable_dmarket_arbitrage = enable_dmarket_arbitrage\n        self.enable_cross_platform = enable_cross_platform\n\n        # Storage for discovered opportunities and listing targets\n        self.opportunities: list[ArbitrageOpportunity] = []\n        self.dmarket_only_opportunities: list[dict[str, Any]] = []  # DMarket-only arbitrage\n        self.listing_targets: dict[str, WaxpeerListingTarget] = {}  # asset_id -> target"},"thoughtSignature":"CikBjz1rX+va6YwpqXsZGNmLGf4cnImyiagdcs8JHznsS42SRuT8kZk5ZwpFAY89a1/jnN6WzRpY6s49qHnSKYaE00BEzebNA9Cyg+KHuc7ZdsxSga8BHmVAKyYcZn5bcHWtnjrRitCWh838dAX3/Gvr"}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":126411,"output":796,"cacheRead":122866,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127207,"cost":{"input":0.2